it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.ip6

Class Ip6Layer

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.ip6.Ip6Layer

  • public class Ip6Layer
extends java.lang.Object
    IPv6 layer provides standard IPv6 service to upper layers.

    It includes basic ICMPv6 support.
